OL,3,CPrince Harry reflects on mother's
OL,4,Clegacy as he walks in Ukraine minefield
OL,6,FPrince Harry told ITV News The Halo
OL,7,FTrust was doing 'incredible work'
OL,8,Fclearing minefields from Bucha left by
OL,9,Fretreating Russian forces.
OL,11,FPrince Harry has entered an active
OL,12,Fminefield in Ukraine and spoken of his
OL,13,Fsadness that 30 years after his
OL,14,Fmother's famous trip to Angola, yet
OL,15,Fanother cleanup is underway in a
OL,16,Fconflict zone.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
