OL,3,CPrince Harry reflects on mother's
OL,4,Clegacy as he walks in Ukraine minefield
OL,6,FThe Duke of Sussex was driven an hour
OL,7,Ffrom the capital Kyiv to the town of
OL,8,FBucha, where Russian forces are
OL,9,Faccused of appalling acts of
OL,10,Finhumanity when they occupied this
OL,11,Ftown in 2022.
OL,13,FIt was a moment when Harry followed in
OL,14,Fthe footsteps of Princess Diana, who
OL,15,Fhighlighted the work of the demining
OL,16,Fcharity, The Halo Trust, by walking in
OL,17,Fan Angolan minefield in 1997.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
