OL,3,CPrince Harry reflects on mother's
OL,4,Clegacy as he walks in Ukraine minefield
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe workload for the deminers in
OL,12,FUkraine is vast, and Ukraine is now
OL,13,FThe Halo Trust's biggest operation
OL,14,Fanywhere in the world.
OL,16,FHarry left Kyiv as the sun was rising
OL,17,Fand arrived at the demining site where
OL,18,Fhe saw what he called the "incredible
OL,19,Fwork" the charity is working to make
OL,20,Fthe area safe.
OL,26,@zD@[OU{D@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
