OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777104370
OL,3,CPrince Harry reflects on mother's
OL,4,Clegacy as he walks in Ukraine minefield
OL,6,F"What Halo Trust is doing is
OL,7,Fabsolutely incredible work", the Duke
OL,8,Fof Sussex told ITV News after his
OL,9,Fvisit.
OL,11,F"It's sad, it's very, very sad because
OL,12,Fnearly 30 years ago, my mother was in
OL,13,FAngola, here we are again in a new
OL,14,Fconflict."
OL,16,FPrince Harry spoke to Royal Editor,
OL,17,FChris Ship, about the necessary work
OL,18,Fof The Halo Trust
OL,26,@oD@[O]vD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
