OL,3,CPrince Harry reflects on mother's
OL,4,Clegacy as he walks in Ukraine minefield
OL,6,FThis was where Ukrainian forces pushed
OL,7,Fback Russian troops at the start of
OL,8,Fthe full-scale invasion in 2022. As
OL,9,Fthey retreated, thousands of pieces of
OL,10,FRussian ammunition and ordnance were
OL,11,Fleft scattered on the battlefield.
OL,13,FIn other sites we visited with The
OL,14,FHalo Trust in Ukraine this week, the
OL,15,Fmine clearance work is focused on
OL,16,Flandmines the Russian forces
OL,17,Fdeliberately laid - some to target
OL,18,Fpeople, others to target tanks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
