OL,3,CPrince Harry reflects on mother's
OL,4,Clegacy as he walks in Ukraine minefield
OL,6,FBack in the woods, Harry was shown
OL,7,Fsome of the modern technology The Halo
OL,8,FTrust now uses to help with their
OL,9,Fimmense task in Ukraine.
OL,11,FIt includes drones that can clearly
OL,12,Fdetect mines or ammunition on the
OL,13,Fground and high-technology robots that
OL,14,Fcan enter a minefield ahead of any
OL,15,Fhuman.
OL,17,FHarry knows that his visit will help
OL,18,Fto keep alive the legacy of his late
OL,19,Fmother, who died shortly after her
OL,20,Fvisit to Angola in 1997.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
