PN,31610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777104370
OL,3,CPrince Harry reflects on mother's
OL,4,Clegacy as he walks in Ukraine minefield
OL,6,FIn a speech in Kyiv on Thursday, he
OL,7,Falso echoed the words of Princess
OL,8,FDiana, who said in Angola that she was
OL,9,F"not a political figure" but a
OL,10,Fhumanitarian one.
OL,12,FHarry said to the Kyiv Security Forum:
OL,13,F"I am not here as a politician. I am
OL,14,Fhere as a soldier who understands
OL,15,Fservice, as a humanitarian."
OL,17,FThe Halo Trust employs 1,300 people in
OL,18,FUkraine for mine clearance.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@XO]uD@AOU
