OL,3,CPrince Harry reflects on mother's
OL,4,Clegacy as he walks in Ukraine minefield
OL,6,F"It's sad, it's depressing but thank
OL,7,FGod for Halo Trust", the prince told
OL,8,Fus today.
OL,10,FThis is the Talking Royals - our
OL,11,Fweekly podcast about the Royal Family,
OL,12,Fwith ITV News Royal Editor Chris Ship
OL,13,Fand Producer Lizzie Robinson.
